<br />

<br />
While I will say I like this BP, it has a 1492 point cost on it.  I can buy the Everfrost BP with slightly lesser stats for half the cost.  Basically, I can buy the EF BP and augment it for the price of only buying the NRo (Royal Attendant's) BP.  This means I can get more pieces faster.  
